  <name>Nautune</name>
  <summary>Poseidon's Music Player for Jellyfin</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      Nautune is a beautiful, deep-sea themed music player designed specifically for Jellyfin.
      Built with Flutter, it offers a native experience with smooth audio playback and deep server integration.
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Gapless playback and intelligent pre-loading.</li>
      <li>Full Jellyfin integration: Sync playlists, favorites, and recent tracks.</li>
      <li>Offline support: Download your library for listening anywhere.</li>
      <li>Direct Play: Stream original quality FLAC, AAC, and MP3 without transcoding.</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

